1. *Martin* je nedavno počeo da uči strani jezik. (Martin recently started to learn a foreign language.)
2. Svi su čekali *Martina* da počne priču. (Everyone was waiting for Martin to start the story.)
3. *Martina* slušalice su joj bile skupe, ali vredne. (Martin's headphones were expensive, but worth it.)
4. *Martina* majka mu je poklonila knjigu. (Martin's mother gave him a book as a gift.)
5. *Martinu* je bilo teško da ostvari svoj san. (It was hard for Martin to achieve his dream.)